### POST /api/encryption/decrypt

This endpoint is used to decrypt encrypted data using the specified initialization vector (IV) and authentication tag.

#### Request Body

- `encryptedData` (string): The encrypted data to be decrypted.

- `iv` (string): The initialization vector used for encryption.

- `authTag` (string): The authentication tag used for encryption.


